          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1629467803214-x200.jpg",
